  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">STEM education 2017-18</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The STEM Education Programme will support knowledge exchange and partnership opportunities between the UK and India on STEM education approaches and in doing so build the human resource capacity in a vital area for economic development and social wellbeing.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">These workshops will train and create awareness among experienced teachers  to use research based pedagogical tools  in their colleges in the areas of Physics, Chemistry, Biology, Mathematics and Earth Sciences</narrative>
  </description>
